title: Commission Regulation (EEC) No 200/93 of 29 January 1993 repealing Regulation (EEC) No 3053/92 prolonging the second suspension of the advance fixing of the import levy for certain cereals
header:
COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 200/93 of 29 January 1993 repealing Regulation (EEC) No 3053/92 prolonging the second suspension of the advance fixing of the import levy for certain cereals
THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES
main_body: Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3053/92 is hereby repealed.

This Regulation shall enter into force on 1 February 1993.
This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States.
attachments:
Done at Brussels, 29 January 1993.
For the Commission
RenĂŠ STEICHEN
Member of the Commission
